"Quia respexit", Joseph.

1109
01:44:19,860 --> 01:44:20,970
Someday, you know,

1110
01:44:22,430 --> 01:44:24,690
he who is your father may forget you.

1111
01:44:26,370 --> 01:44:29,570
Then you'll regret I’m not around.

1112
01:44:42,780 --> 01:44:43,770
Look at me!

1113
01:44:46,830 --> 01:44:48,930
I am He who is.

1114
01:44:49,090 --> 01:44:50,740
Quit clowning! Get in!

1115
01:44:50,820 --> 01:44:51,730
No!

1116
01:44:52,080 --> 01:44:54,820
I must tend to my father's affairs.

1117
01:44:56,460 --> 01:44:58,580
By God, we'll see about that.

1118
01:45:00,270 --> 01:45:01,320
No, stop it!

1119
01:45:02,780 --> 01:45:03,940
Stop it!

1120
01:45:05,420 --> 01:45:06,570
He'll be back.

1121
01:45:19,520 --> 01:45:20,310
When?

1122
01:45:20,680 --> 01:45:21,470
At Easter.

1123
01:45:22,180 --> 01:45:23,410
or Trinity Sunday.

1124
01:45:55,660 --> 01:45:56,570
Lady...

1125
01:46:01,460 --> 01:46:02,920
Hello, lady!

1126
01:46:03,970 --> 01:46:05,230
What is it?

1127
01:46:05,230 --> 01:46:08,320
Nothing. Hail, Mary.

1128
01:47:36,110 --> 01:47:37,580
I am of the Virgin,

1129
01:47:39,100 --> 01:47:40,720
and I didn't want this being.

1130
01:47:41,770 --> 01:47:43,400
I only left my imprint on
the soul that helped me.

1131
01:47:44,450 --> 01:47:45,220
That's all.

